==Accolades== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders sortable" |- !scope="col"| Year !scope="col"| Award !scope="col"| Category !scope="col"| Nominated work !scope="col"| Result ! scope="col" class="unsortable"| {{Abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}} |- | 1998 ! scope="row" | Aafathis Awards – 1998 | Best Actress | ''[[Amaanaaiy]]'' | {{won}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=JamsheedhaAward>{{cite news|url=https://presidency.gov.mv/NationalAwards/Winner/417 |title=National Award of Recognition 2003 – Jamsheedha Ahmed |work=Presidency Maldives |language=Divehi |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102074017/https://presidency.gov.mv/NationalAwards/Winner/417 |url-status=live |archivedate=30 October 2020 |accessdate=30 October 2020}}</ref> |- | 2004 ! scope="row" | National Award of Recognition | colspan="2"|Performing Arts - Acting | {{won}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=JamsheedhaAward/> |- | rowspan="2"| 2007 ! scope="row" | 3rd [[Gaumee Film Awards]] | [[Gaumee Film Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]] | ''[[Amaanaaiy]]'' | {{won}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=mihaaru/> |- ! scope="row"| [[4th Gaumee Film Awards]] | [[Gaumee Film Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]] | ''[[Vehey Vaarey Therein]]'' | {{nom}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=GFA4won/> |- |}
